  <brief_title>An In-vitro Real-time System Based on Tissue Smears to Identify Malignancy During Hysteroscopic Procedure</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Development of an In-vitro Real-time System Based on Tissue Smears to Identify Malignancy During Hysteroscopic Procedure Using FTIR-ATR Spectroscopy</official_title>
