  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the current study is to develop a near real-time system using infrared
      spectroscopy, that will evaluate the histological specimen that was removed from the uterine
      cavity during the hysteroscopy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
